              <li><strong>Community sourcing</strong> · "nominate a brand" per city</li>
              <li><strong>Local calendar</strong> · Bathukamma in Hyderabad, Pongal in Chennai</li>
              <li><strong>Micro-assortment</strong> · core fixed, flex by neighbourhood</li>
